<TITLE>#466: 08-09-00 DEPUTY ATTORNEY GENERAL HOLDER TO HONOR CIVIL RIGHTS PIONEER RUBY
BRIDGES AT CEREMONY AT CORCORAN GALLERY OF ART</TITLE>
</HEAD>

